<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[What did you think of the ending of The Storyteller. I saw the twist coming quite a bit before the end. I didn't like the ending and didn't think Sage's character would have done what she did if she was true to her own beliefs and did not want to be haunted by her decision. What do you think? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
